query.description: Executables that are not ending on traditional extensions.

query.query: (app_proto:"smb" OR app_proto:"http"  OR app_proto:"nfs"  OR app_proto:"ftp" OR app_proto:"smtp") AND (fileinfo.type:"executable") AND NOT (fileinfo.filename.keyword:*.exe OR fileinfo.filename.keyword:*.dll OR fileinfo.filename.keyword:*.com)

query.title: Hidden Executables -1
